title: Stuck on authenticating
body:
On my way logging in I get stuck on Authenticating. Tried different account. Couldn't log in there either... Anyone with the same problem?
(changed place where the discussion is)

replies.body: We were having a few issues with our EU authentication servers earlier today, but it looks like that should be smoothed out at this point! Hit us back if you're still having troubles getting logged in and we can take a closer look.
i have the same problem, from sweden. I cant login to my och my friends accounts on eu nordic and east. but i can login to my account on eu west..
The same thing happen to me . I'm from Sweden . Please fix it !
